sentences.english: How to defense collusive attack is the key problems for the designing of fingerprinting.

sentences.english: The fingerprints found on the gun were used to convict her.
sentences.chinese: 枪上发现的指纹被用来判明她有罪。

sentences.english: A minute examination revealed fingerprints on a glass.
sentences.chinese: 经详细检查后发现一只玻璃杯上留有指纹印。

sentences.english: Because fingerprints are produced by a combination of genetic programming and random chance.
sentences.chinese: 因为指纹的生成由基因规律和随意组合决定。

sentences.english: The burglars wore rubber gloves to guard against fingerprints.
sentences.chinese: 盗贼戴著橡皮手套以防留下指纹印。

sentences.english: Fingerprint identification procedures, including binarization, thinning, such as extraction of feature points.

sentences.english: The space monkeys are using lye to burn off their fingerprints.

sentences.english: The last work is an installation of fingerprint stamp.

sentences.english: Every humpback has a different pattern of spots, just as human fingerprints are all different.
sentences.chinese: 每头座头鲸的尾部斑点都不同，就如同人类的指纹。

sentences.english: Having no fingerprints would really be a nightmare for most of us.
sentences.chinese: 对大多数人来说，没有指纹真的会是一场噩梦。

sentences.english: ConclusionThe fingerprint established can be used for quality control of Hainan Naucleae officinalis.

sentences.english: RESULTS The HPLC fingerprint of the Fructus Tribulus terrestris L. was established preliminarily.
